直系の既知のサブクラス:
YamlArray
public class CollectionList<V> extends AbstractArrayCollectionList<V> implements ICollectionList<V>, Cloneable, Serializable
This CollectionList provides a better feature than just a List or ArrayList, like using #map without using the Stream. Additionally, this list provides the some useful methods. This list is based on the ArrayList and you may not get the performance advantages by using this list. This list just provides the useful methods.
